<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">ل ث ي:</span> <span class="c2">(اللِّثَةُ)</span> بِالتَّخْفِيفِ مَا حَوْلَ الْأَسْنَانِ وَجَمْعُهَا <span class="c2">(لِثَاثٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(لِثًى)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>